I am getting this issue in custom coded workflow

so the error is, that you have hit the 10secondly api ratelimit. most likely you have enrolled many entities in a workflow that makes requests to the HubSpot api. depending on the license your 10secondly is 100/10 seconds or 150/10 seconds.
so that means you can make up to 150 requests per 10 seconds. did you enroll a lot into this workflow? or are you doing many request inside this one workflow?
do we have any api of the deals from where I can get all the deals with pipeline and associated labels ?

For the deals there is an api to get all, get one by object_id or search for deals with filters.

For the pipeline <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/crm/pipelines|https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/crm/pipelines>
